#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:2
#: 5461de6dfc104a9d8a25aa80b24e873e
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "安装"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:4
#: 9cd7789aa38f4cb1896a14fb7078d172
msgid ""
"TensorMesh runs on Linux, macOS, and Windows. The only hard requirements are"
" **Python ≥ 3.10** and **PyTorch ≥ 2.0**; everything else (NumPy, SciPy, "
"meshio, ``torch-sla``, ...) is pulled in automatically by ``pip``."
msgstr ""
"TensorMesh 可在 Linux、macOS 和 Windows 上运行。唯一的硬性要求是 **Python ≥ 3.10** 和 "
"**PyTorch ≥ 2.0**\\ ；其余所有依赖（NumPy、SciPy、meshio、\\ ``torch-sla`` 等）都会由 "
"``pip`` 自动安装。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:8
#: 77b224b0e1c34bde81680764dcf8553e
msgid ""
"If you plan to use the GPU backend, install a CUDA-enabled PyTorch build "
"*before* installing TensorMesh — follow the official `PyTorch installation "
"selector <https://pytorch.org/get-started/locally/>`_ for the right command "
"on your platform / CUDA version."
msgstr ""
"如果你打算使用 GPU 后端，请在安装 TensorMesh *之前* 先安装启用了 CUDA 的 PyTorch 版本——请按照官方的 "
"`PyTorch 安装选择器 <https://pytorch.org/get-started/locally/>`_\\ ，针对你的平台／CUDA "
"版本获取正确的安装命令。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:15
#: 07bde82298204205bdeb3cb517e46406
msgid "Install via PyPI"
msgstr "通过 PyPI 安装"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:17
#: c2028a6ae0694f949c74821f02d30fc6
msgid "The recommended way to install TensorMesh is from PyPI:"
msgstr "推荐通过 PyPI 来安装 TensorMesh："

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:24
#: fc8e060c91fc40d2b44a2ef7cda37f4f
msgid ""
"Use the second form if you have an NVIDIA GPU and want the CUDA sparse-"
"solver backends — the ``[gpu]`` extra pulls in both CuPy and cuDSS through "
"``torch-sla``. The quotes are needed because ``[...]`` is a shell glob "
"character; see `Sparse solvers and GPU acceleration`_ for the per-backend "
"breakdown if you only want one of CuPy or cuDSS."
msgstr ""
"如果你拥有 NVIDIA GPU 并想使用 CUDA 稀疏求解器后端，请使用第二种形式——``[gpu]`` 这个 extra 会通过 ``torch-"
"sla`` 同时安装 CuPy 和 cuDSS。这里需要加引号，因为 ``[...]`` 是 shell 的通配符字符；如果你只想要 CuPy 或 "
"cuDSS 中的一个，请参阅 `Sparse solvers and GPU acceleration`_ 了解各后端的细分说明。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:30
#: 6dcba5dcf845459a88d629f5717aaed8
msgid ""
"Either form pulls in all required dependencies, including `torch-sla "
"<https://www.torchsla.com/>`_, the differentiable sparse linear algebra "
"library that powers TensorMesh's solvers. The base ``pip install tensor-"
"mesh`` installs only the **CPU** sparse stack (SciPy / native PyTorch); see "
"`Sparse solvers and GPU acceleration`_ below for the full extras matrix "
"(``[cupy]`` / ``[cudss]`` / ``[gpu]``) and how to verify which backends are "
"usable on your machine."
msgstr ""
"两种形式都会安装所有必需的依赖，包括 `torch-sla <https://www.torchsla.com/>`_——这是为 TensorMesh "
"求解器提供动力的可微稀疏线性代数库。基础的 ``pip install tensor-mesh`` 只会安装 **CPU** 稀疏栈（SciPy / "
"原生 PyTorch）；完整的 extras 矩阵（\\ ``[cupy]`` / ``[cudss]`` / ``[gpu]``\\ "
"）以及如何验证你的机器上有哪些后端可用，请参阅下文的 `Sparse solvers and GPU acceleration`_\\ 。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:40
#: b27012e160c44f37820bf71b2677da36
msgid "Install from source"
msgstr "从源码安装"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:42
#: 18f41d8bf31047e98ad27d5c39fce6c4
msgid ""
"For development work, or to get the latest unreleased changes, clone the "
"repository and install in editable mode:"
msgstr "如需进行开发工作，或获取尚未发布的最新改动，请克隆仓库并以可编辑模式安装："

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:51
#: 1148b7bdeda9455c8c2b192c841645b8
msgid ""
"The ``-e`` (editable) flag means edits to the source tree are picked up "
"without reinstalling. To install with the test dependencies as well:"
msgstr "``-e``\\ （可编辑）标志意味着对源码树的修改会被自动识别，无需重新安装。若要同时安装测试依赖："

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:60
#: e24f40e8fb544f38b95c430ee982305f
msgid "Sparse solvers and GPU acceleration"
msgstr "稀疏求解器与 GPU 加速"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:62
#: 42881e93418844dd9604e653177c74ce
msgid ""
"The sparse linear-algebra layer that powers TensorMesh's solvers lives in a "
"standalone library, `torch-sla <https://www.torchsla.com/>`_, so that it can"
" evolve independently and serve other projects. ``torch-sla`` is a **hard, "
"import-time** dependency — :mod:`tensormesh.sparse` will not import without "
"it — and is the canonical entry point for both CPU and GPU sparse solves. "
"All current and future solver work lands in ``torch-sla`` first; we "
"recommend keeping it up to date."
msgstr ""
"为 TensorMesh 求解器提供动力的稀疏线性代数层位于一个独立的库 `torch-sla "
"<https://www.torchsla.com/>`_ 中，这样它便能独立演进并服务于其他项目。\\ ``torch-sla`` 是一个 "
"**硬性的、导入时即需满足** 的依赖——缺少它 :mod:`tensormesh.sparse` 将无法导入——并且它是 CPU 和 GPU "
"稀疏求解的统一入口。当前和未来的所有求解器工作都会先落地到 ``torch-sla``\\ ；我们建议保持其为最新版本。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:70
#: 07298eb2f77449e99724283d551c992b
msgid ""
"The base ``tensor-mesh`` wheel only pulls the **CPU** stack (SciPy / native "
"PyTorch). To enable a GPU backend, install one of the mirrored extras:"
msgstr ""
"基础的 ``tensor-mesh`` wheel 只会安装 **CPU** 栈（SciPy / 原生 PyTorch）。若要启用 GPU "
"后端，请安装其中一个镜像的 extra："

